title: Skye
description:
Ello' I'm Skye I like to draw, stream, make videos and play games!
I've been around in the community since January 2019, been in competitive since September 2019, & have been Staffing tournaments since March 2020.

Usually I tend to lurk but if you approach me i'll definitely be willing to talk, since I like meeting new people and making new friends!

♡Oh yea and I love working with the people in IPL that I get to work with at IPL♡
♡uwu♡

title: Snek
description: Former competitive player of Enlightenment, and former head TO of Squid Spawning Grounds, I am an avid supporter of the competitive scene that does his best to further the scene however i can, but when I'm not you can usually find me on Phantasy Star Online 2.

title: Froppy♪
description: A Competitive Splatoon 2 player who has been working from the bottom up. I don't get lucky, I earn everything that has come my way. I coach, help, and play with the lower level competitive community a lot.
